1
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:12,480
Calling the police again

2
00:01:12,720 --> 00:01:14,280
was just to make us suspect

3
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:15,920
that you are the killer.

4
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:19,920
Shen Man.

5
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,640
You are not the killer.

6
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:31,480
I can understand.

7
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:34,520
To find out the truth about your sister's suicide,

8
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:35,440
you took a risk.

9
00:01:36,160 --> 00:01:37,720
But misleading the police like this...

10
00:01:37,720 --> 00:01:39,240
You know, what can you understand about me?

11
00:01:42,520 --> 00:01:43,360
Can you understand

12
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:44,960
the pain of losing my sister?

13
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:48,960
Do you know Shen Qing?

14
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:50,520
I'm telling you,

15
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:53,120
there is no way she committed suicide.

16
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:56,480
No matter the cost,

17
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:58,200
I will find

18
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,680
the truth about my sister's death.

19
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:17,160
My dad used to be a police officer too.

20
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:21,360
Later, he got involved in a murder case.

21
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:24,160
All the evidence pointed to him.

22
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:25,480
But I firmly believe

23
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:26,920
he didn't kill anyone.

24
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:31,120
Now that I've become a police officer,

25
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:33,760
I will keep investigating

26
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:35,040
until I find out the truth.

27
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,560
Shen Man.

28
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:45,560
I understand you very well.

29
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,960
I hope you can make amends

30
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,320
by helping us.

31
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:53,320
Let's find the killer together.

32
00:03:01,480 --> 00:03:03,040
Not charging her with obstruction of justice

33
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:04,320
is already generous enough.

34
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:06,120
What use can she be?

35
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:06,680
Team Leader.

36
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:09,120
The killer staged Ai Xia's death

37
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,840
to look related to occult arts.

38
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,960
It must point to something.

39
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:14,760
And Shen Man is a blogger who studies occult arts.

40
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:15,760
You said it yourself,

41
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,480
as long as we can solve the case,

42
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:19,120
you don't care about the means.

43
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:26,960
Why should I help you?

44
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:30,960
This card

45
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:33,120
was found when we searched your home.

46
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:38,680
The pattern on the card matches the pattern

47
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,000
on the clay sculpture at the crime scene.

48
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:54,360
This is the tattoo on my sister's body.

49
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:59,320
The pattern on the card...

50
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:01,320
The police haven't released it to the public.

51
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:02,880
This means

52
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:04,520
the person who sent you the card

53
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:06,000
is most likely the killer.

54
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:08,160
Why would the killer

55
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,200
send this to me?

56
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:12,360
He knows Shen Qing's tattoo.

57
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:17,000
What exactly is his relationship with Shen Qing?

58
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,760
Catch the killer,

59
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:22,640
and you'll get the answers you want.

60
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:04,360
Get up.

61
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:05,520
Pack me up and take me with you, sis.

62
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:07,480
Stop fooling around.

63
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:36,840
Where do we start?

64
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,080
The crime scene.

65
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:41,640
If there really were gods protecting us,

66
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:44,200
Dr. Ai Xia wouldn't have died so horribly.

67
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:46,760
Go ahead.

68
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:49,040
On the day of the crime,

69
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,760
how did you get here during the day?

70
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:51,840
And what did you do?

71
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:53,480
Tell me everything in detail.

72
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:56,840
Start from the beginning.

73
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:57,840
Start from the beginning.

74
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:15,320
Hey, I was here first.

75
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:41,640
Wait a minute.

76
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:45,200
You don't need to go back that far.

77
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:47,600
Just start from when you entered the hospital.

78
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:55,920
Homage to the Supreme Arhat,

79
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:57,600
the Perfectly Enlightened One.

80
00:08:57,600 --> 00:09:00,080
May all bad luck and omens stay far from life,

81
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:02,280
whether from accidents or human malice.

82
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:03,640
Free from failure and danger.

83
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:05,080
Respectfully inviting The Three Jewels,

84
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:06,720
to grant safety to the wearer.

85
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:16,920
Where are you?

86
00:09:17,920 --> 00:09:18,720
Over there.

87
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,080
What are you doing here?

88
00:09:28,520 --> 00:09:29,200
Sorry,

89
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:31,320
occupational hazard kicked in.

90
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:39,480
Stop.

91
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:42,960
All these things you're saying,

92
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,200
what do they have to do with the case?

93
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,320
You said

94
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,920
to start from when I entered the hospital.

95
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,040
You are the police.

96
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:49,440
Whether it's related to the case,

97
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,760
that's for you to judge.

98
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:56,600
Then start from when you entered

99
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:58,840
Dr. Ai Xia's office.

100
00:09:59,320 --> 00:09:59,920
Okay.

101
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:15,520
Speak up.

102
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:16,760
There's nothing else.

103
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,640
After I entered the office,

104
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:20,120
I put the phone there to record secretly.

105
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,240
Then I just left.

106
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:27,120
You're doing this on purpose, aren't you?

107
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:30,640
All that irrelevant nonsense earlier,

108
00:10:30,640 --> 00:10:31,520
you described in such detail.

109
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:32,400
But when it comes to Ai Xia,

110
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:33,000
nothing.

111
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,520
Well, there really wasn't anything.

112
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:36,640
Dr. Ai Xia wasn't there when I arrived.

113
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:41,920
Where did you hide the phone?

114
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:43,800
There.

115
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,120
Is anyone here?

116
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:53,280
I'm coming in.

117
00:10:59,520 --> 00:11:00,440
Hello.

118
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:06,160
Anyone here?

119
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:58,640
The police didn't find the phone at the scene.

120
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:03,040
If the killer took it,

121
00:12:04,040 --> 00:12:05,520
it must have recorded something.

122
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:09,640
We'll know once we find it.

123
00:12:09,640 --> 00:12:10,560
I have the location.

124
00:12:19,360 --> 00:12:21,240
The GPS shows it's right under the bridge ahead.

125
00:12:21,400 --> 00:12:22,160
Okay.

126
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:14,040
Shen Man.

127
00:13:14,280 --> 00:13:15,040
Coming.

128
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:20,800
It's softer here than the rest.

129
00:13:20,920 --> 00:13:22,360
It must have been disturbed recently.

130
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:31,760
Dig.

131
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:34,120
No, no, no.

132
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,240
I'm not a police officer.

133
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,160
What's buried down here

134
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:38,240
is important physical evidence.

135
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:39,560
If I damage it while digging,

136
00:13:39,560 --> 00:13:40,560
that wouldn't be good.

137
00:14:09,920 --> 00:14:10,800
It's ruined.

138
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:14,240
The killer was in such a hurry to destroy evidence,

139
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:16,920
which means the phone definitely recorded something.

140
00:14:17,400 --> 00:14:19,280
Once we repair it, we'll have new leads.

141
00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:24,280
Besides burning the phone,

142
00:14:24,280 --> 00:14:25,520
the killer burned other things too.

143
00:14:30,120 --> 00:14:31,000
What is this?

144
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:42,760
To recover the data,

145
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:44,880
ordinary digital shops can't handle this.

146
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:48,880
Don't worry.

147
00:14:49,040 --> 00:14:49,760
Leave it to me.

148
00:14:49,920 --> 00:14:50,440
Let's go.

149
00:15:27,640 --> 00:15:28,280
Shen Man

150
00:15:29,120 --> 00:15:29,560
You...

151
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:31,160
You just won't stop, will you?

152
00:15:31,880 --> 00:15:33,240
Chasing me to record a show again.

153
00:15:34,520 --> 00:15:36,000
What is it this time?

154
00:15:45,880 --> 00:15:47,160
No problem, right, Da Jin?

155
00:15:47,760 --> 00:15:50,400
If you have trouble, find Da Jin.

156
00:15:50,400 --> 00:15:51,520
Just rest assured.

157
00:15:57,560 --> 00:15:58,240
By the way,

158
00:15:58,640 --> 00:16:00,760
that guy at the door, Zan-something-Nan...

159
00:16:00,760 --> 00:16:01,680
Why are you looking for him?

160
00:16:01,680 --> 00:16:02,920
He's just a big scammer.

161
00:16:03,920 --> 00:16:06,440
My right shoulder has been hurting lately.

162
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,600
The Master said it must be...

163
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:09,160
that something is following me.

164
00:16:12,280 --> 00:16:13,440
God knows.

165
00:16:13,920 --> 00:16:16,240
It must be that day you took me to film,

166
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:17,680
and I encountered some unclean thing.

167
00:16:17,680 --> 00:16:18,520
Let me tell you,

168
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:19,880
I'm telling you,

169
00:16:19,880 --> 00:16:21,400
if I don't find the Master to break the spell,

170
00:16:21,400 --> 00:16:22,520
I won't be able to...

171
00:16:22,520 --> 00:16:24,240
enter my happy life.

172
00:16:24,280 --> 00:16:25,240
Nonsense.

173
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:26,440
It hurts! Don't touch me.

174
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:28,240
You're just having a flare-up of frozen shoulder.

175
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:29,680
Next time I'll give you an address.

176
00:16:29,680 --> 00:16:30,960
You let that blind man Old Sun

177
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:32,120
do some bone-setting for you again.

178
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:33,360
What blind man Old Sun?

179
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:34,680
That blind man is faking it.

180
00:16:34,680 --> 00:16:35,560
And you believe that?

181
00:16:35,680 --> 00:16:37,000
Shen Man is a murderer.

182
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,760
Doctor Ai Xia was killed by her.

183
00:16:38,760 --> 00:16:39,640
You have to believe me.

184
00:16:39,640 --> 00:16:41,120
She is the kind of person who does things like that.

185
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:42,160
I'm really not lying to you.

186
00:16:42,160 --> 00:16:43,920
Shen Man is a murderer!

187
00:16:43,920 --> 00:16:45,280
She's a killer, you know.

188
00:16:45,280 --> 00:16:46,360
Spreading rumors about others...

189
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:47,880
do you know you can be held legally responsible?

190
00:16:48,280 --> 00:16:49,560
Back then, didn't you police

191
00:16:49,560 --> 00:16:50,640
also think it was her?

192
00:16:51,800 --> 00:16:53,080
Shen Man's suspicion of murder

193
00:16:53,080 --> 00:16:54,240
has already been ruled out by the police.

194
00:16:54,560 --> 00:16:55,920
If you dare to spread rumors again,

195
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:57,880
it won't be as simple as today.

196
00:17:03,920 --> 00:17:05,160
Between you and Shen Man,

197
00:17:05,160 --> 00:17:06,160
what exactly is the grudge?

198
00:17:06,280 --> 00:17:08,280
You know that supernatural video account of hers...

199
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:09,880
She and I can be considered

200
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:10,920
half-colleagues, I guess.

201
00:17:11,640 --> 00:17:13,040
I don't know for what reason

202
00:17:13,040 --> 00:17:14,440
she secretly films me all the time.

203
00:17:15,360 --> 00:17:16,240
And my disciples...

204
00:17:16,240 --> 00:17:17,400
she exposes them in various ways.

205
00:17:17,400 --> 00:17:19,920
Whenever I see her, I get angry.

206
00:17:27,760 --> 00:17:29,120
Do you know what this is?

207
00:17:30,040 --> 00:17:31,360
This is a type of occult arts.

208
00:17:31,520 --> 00:17:34,160
The victim of the spell enters Avīci Hell.

209
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:35,760
Avīci Hell?

210
00:17:37,040 --> 00:17:38,400
Is there any specific meaning to this?

211
00:17:38,560 --> 00:17:40,680
Avīci Hell is the deepest level of hell.

212
00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:41,680
Suffering without interruption.

213
00:17:41,680 --> 00:17:42,880
Never to be liberated.

214
00:17:43,360 --> 00:17:44,160
But I heard

215
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:46,120
only those who harm children

216
00:17:46,120 --> 00:17:47,640
enter the deepest level of hell.

217
00:17:51,280 --> 00:17:52,280
You can go now.

218
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:02,440
The killer removed Ai Xia's uterus.

219
00:18:03,280 --> 00:18:04,920
Could it be that all this is related to children?

220
00:18:07,400 --> 00:18:08,120
It's done.
